channel.title: Problem with downloading WinRar, please help!

So i cant play on the new client and i cannot buy winrar because i dont have a credit card, or i dont want to spend 40 frikken bucks. PLEASE someone help me, i really want to play on silabsoft's sick new client like everyone else.
thanks a bunch
